<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Bootstrap 4 Website Example</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link href="https://gitcdn.github.io/bootstrap-toggle/2.2.2/css/bootstrap-toggle.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.0.12/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-G0fIWCsCzJIMAVNQPfjH08cyYaUtMwjJwqiRKxxE/rx96Uroj1BtIQ6MLJuheaO9" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<style>
/* Bootstrap Toggle v2.2.2 corrections for Bootsrtap 4*/
.toggle-off {
  box-shadow: inset 0 3px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .125);
}
.toggle.off {
  border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .25);
}
.toggle-handle {
  background-color: white;
  border: thin rgba(0, 0, 0, .25) solid;
}
</style>
<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-dark navbar-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">*.net.ict.e.titech.ac.jp</a>
    <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapsibleNavbar">
      <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
    </button>
    <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="collapsibleNavbar">
      <span class="navbar-text mr-auto">Production environment</span>
      <ul class="navbar-nav">
        <li class="nav-item">
          <a class="nav-link" href="https://github.com/mi2428"><span class="fa fa-code-branch pr-1" aria-hidden="true"></span>GitHub</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="container mt-3">
  <h2><span class="fa fa-plus-square pr-2"></span>Register new record</h2>
  <p>Select record type, input domain name and record value, and select TTL. Comment is optional.
    If the domain name does not end with <code>.</code> then <code>.net.ict.e.titech.ac.jp.</code> is appended to the end.</p>
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
      <label for="new-record-type">Type</label>
      <select class="form-control" id="new-record-type">
        <option>A  (IPv4 address)</option>
        <option>CNAME (Canonical name)</option>
        <option>MX (Mail exchange)</option>
        <option>AAAA (IPv6 address)</option>
        <option>TXT (Text)</option>
        <option>PTR (Pointer)</option>
        <option>SRV (Service locator)</option>
        <option>SPF (Sender Policy Framework)</option>
        <option>NS (Name server)</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 mb-3">
      <label for="new-record-name">Name</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="new-record-name" required>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
      <label for="new-record-value">Value</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="new-record-value" placeholder="" required>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="col-md-10 mb-9">
      <label for="new-record-comment">Comment</label>
      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="new-record-comment">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2 mb-3">
      <label for="new-record-tty">TTL</label>
      <select class="form-control" id="new-record-type">
        <option>60 (1min)</option>
        <option>300 (5min)</option>
        <option>3600 (1hour)</option>
        <option>86400 (1day)</option>
      </select>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card mb-3" style="border-left: 5px solid #1b809e;">
    <div class="card-body p-3">
      <h2 class="card-panel-h2" style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #1b809e;">SPF Record</h2>
      <p class="m-0">For information about SPF record format, refer to the applicable documentation. Enter multiple values on separate lines. Enclose values in quotation marks.</p>
      <p class="m-0">Value is like <code>v=spf1 ip4:192.168.0.1/16-all</code></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="d-flex flex-row-reverse">
    <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit"><span class="fa fa-check-circle pr-2"></span>Register record</button>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h2><span class="fa fa-edit pr-2"></span>Edit existing records</h2>
  <p>Type something in the input field to search the table for first names, last names or emails:</p>
  <div class="form-row">
    <div class="col-md-6 mb-12">
      <input class="form-control" id="myInput" type="text" placeholder="Filter..">
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2 mb-12">
      <button class="btn btn-info w-100" type="submit"><span class="fa fa-upload pr-2"></span>Upload zone</button>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2 mb-12">
      <button class="btn btn-success w-100" type="submit"><span class="fa fa-download pr-2"></span>Download zone</button>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2 mb-12">
      <button class="btn btn-danger w-100" type="submit" disabled><span class="fa fa-trash-alt pr-2"></span>Delete selected</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="table-responsive">
    <table class="table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th><input type="checkbox"></th>
          <th>Edit</th>
          <th>Name</th>
          <th>Type</th>
          <th>Value</th>
          <th>TTL</th>
          <th>Enabled</th>
          <th>Comment</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td class="align-middle"><input type="checkbox"></td>
          <td><input type="checkbox" data-toggle="toggle" data-on="<i class='fa fa-lock-open'></i>" data-off="<i class='fa fa-lock'></i>" data-onstyle="info" data-offstyle="success" data-size="normal"></td>
          <td class="align-middle">www.net.ict.e.titech.ac.jp.</td>
          <td class="align-middle">CNAME</td>
          <td class="align-middle">yamaoka-kitaguchi-lab.github.io.</td>
          <td class="align-middle">3600</td>
          <td class="align-middle"><input type="checkbox" checked data-toggle="toggle" data-on="Yes" data-off="No" data-onstyle="success" data-offstyle="danger" disabled></td>
          <td class="align-middle">研究室トップページ (GitHub Pages)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="align-middle"><input type="checkbox"></td>
          <td class="align-middle"><input type="checkbox" data-toggle="toggle" data-on="<i class='fa fa-lock-open'></i>" data-off="<i class='fa fa-lock'></i>" data-onstyle="info" data-offstyle="success" data-size="normal" checked></td>
          <td class="align-middle"><input type="text" class="form-control" value="wiki.net.ict.e.titech.ac.jp." size="30"></td>
          <td class="align-middle">A</td>
          <td class="align-middle"><input type="text" class="form-control" value="131.112.21.133" size="30"></td>
          <td class="align-middle"><input type="text" class="form-control" value="3600" size='10'></td>
          <td class="align-middle"><input type="checkbox" data-toggle="toggle" data-on="Yes" data-off="No" data-onstyle="success" data-offstyle="danger"></td>
          <td class="align-middle"><input type="text" class="form-control" value="研究室Wiki (Kubernetes)"></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <hr>

  <h2><span class="fa fa-history pr-2"></span>Update history</h2>
  <div class="alert alert-success">
    <strong class="pr-2">TBD:</strong>This feature is not implemented.
  </div>
</div>

<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://gitcdn.github.io/bootstrap-toggle/2.2.2/js/bootstrap-toggle.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
